metadata.name: Moomyung
metadata.description:
My original character, Moomyung, is the gatekeeper to hell. 
She stops all those who attempt to escape.  
The king has attempted many times to bring his son back from hell, sending countless soldiers down to seal Moomyung, but to no avail. 
There has yet to be anyone who has been able to thwart Moomyung and get past the gates of hell. 
Will you be the first?
Thank you for reading the long message!

7000*3941 pixel 300dpi
created by bexercube
